title: Why Overeating Doesn't Make You a Failure
itunes:title: Why Overeating Doesn't Make You a Failure
description:
Get the Free Course here:
https://phit.click/freecourse

 

Women often think they are a failure at losing weight just because they haven't successfully kept their weight off. The only thing preventing you today from finally ending your overeating is what goes on in your head. Today I talk about how your past failure can be a valuable asset to your future success.
